text: So I'm not sure the address or the phone number of this place, becaues it's pretty new, and nothing turned up in google, except some Tribune article that wasn't related at all. So i'm not sure the exact addres or phone number or anything. But this is a hotdog stand/ cafe. Which is wonderful, because I love hotdogs and coffee, and this place has both. I've only been here a couple of times but the food is pretty good and it's pretty cheap so what more could you ask for. It would be more like a 3.5 stars, but I'm going to round up.
